ty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20returned%20to%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20after%20turbulence%20injured%20a%20passenger.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20airline%20said%20there%20were%20over%20200%20people%20on%20board%2C%20and%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20was%20on.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESeveral%20carriers%20have%20changed%20protocols%20due%20to%20rising%20concerns%20about%20turbulence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20American%20Airlines%20passenger%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital%20after%20their%20flight%20encountered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbulence-more-frequent-stronger-expert-aviation-explains-why-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturbulence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20Flightradar24%20shows%20that%20Saturday's%20Flight%20930%20from%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20to%20Miami%20U-turned%20less%20than%20two%20hours%20after%20taking%20off.%20It%20ultimately%20became%20a%20four-and-a-half-hour%20flight%20to%20nowhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20airline%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20flight%20landed%20safely%20back%20in%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20%26quot%3Bafter%20encountering%20turbulence%20while%20in%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thank%20our%20crew%20members%20for%20their%20professionalism%20and%20our%20customers%20for%20their%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Boeing%20777%20had%2012%20crew%20members%20and%20221%20passengers%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Brazil%2C%20according%20to%20the%20airline.%20The%20airline%20also%20said%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20was%20on%20when%20the%20plane%20encountered%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favherald.com%2Fh%3Farticle%3D520bc98d%26opt%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Aviation%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20first%20reported%20the%20incident%2C%20said%20the%20passenger%20had