20on%20this%20question%20in%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20Thursday.%20Delhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20is%20now%20a%20tad%20better%20than%20last%20week%20and%20has%20dropped%20to%20the%20'very%20poor'%20band.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20can%20take%20a%20call%20on%20whether%20to%20resume%20physical%20classes%20in%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20and%20other%20cities%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20AG%20Masih%20cracked%20the%20whip%20on%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20warning%20the%20city%20police%20commissioner%20of%20prosecution%20for%20poor%20implementation%20of%20curbs%20to%20tackle%20the%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20today%20noted%20that%20without%20even%20seeing%20any%20report%2C%20it%20can%20say%20that%20no%20checkpoints%20to%20regulate%20vehicles%20are%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%2013%20court-appointed%20commissioners%20who%20monitored%20implementation%20of%20the%20curbs%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20while%20checking%20happened%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20effective%20it%20was.%20The%20counsel%20said%20cops%20were%20%26quot%3Bjumping%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20trucks%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20barricading%20at%20several%20checkpoints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government's%20counsel%20said%20employees%20of%20various%20levels%20were%20deployed%20at%20the%20checkpoints.%20When%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20Delhi%20government%20issued%20specific%20instructions%20to%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20the%20former%20said%20Delhi%20Police%20does%20not%20come%20under%20its%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20asked%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20and%20the%20Centre%20if%20they%20issued%20specific%20instructions%20to%20police.%20It%20was%20told%20that%20orders%20were%20issued%20for%2023%20checkposts.%20The%20court%20asked%20why%20it%20was%20not%20done%20for%20the%20other%20posts.%20%26quot%3BYou%20were%20bound%20to%20post%20officers.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20ask%20the%20Delhi%20police%20commissioner%20to%20be%20penalised%20under%20the%20CAQM%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20it%20is%20apparent%20that%20authorities%20have%20not%20made%20%26quot%3Bearnest%20efforts%26quot%3B%20to%20implement%20the%20curbs%20and%20and%20asked%20CAQM%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20officials%20concerned.%20It%20said%20GRAP%204%20curbs%20were%20not%20implemented%20properly%20and%20proper%20steps%20to%20stop%20trucks%20from%20entering%20Delhi%20were%20not%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20resuming%20physical%20classes%20at%20schools%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20that%20all%20children%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20Internet%20to%20take%20online%20classes.%20The%20court%20has%20asked%20the%20CAQM%20to%20take%20a%20call%20by%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20praised%20the%2013%20Bar%20members%20named%20court%20commissioners%20and%20said%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20and%20submit%20reports%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20apparent%20that%20the%20authorities%20which%20are%20mentioned%20against%20item%20numbers%201%2C%202%20and%203%20of%20stage%204%20of%20GRAP%20have%20made%20no%20earnest%20effort%20to%20implement%20the%20action%20in%20terms%20of%20clauses%201%20-%203.%20Some%20police%20teams%20were%20deputed%20at%20a%20few%20entry%20points%20that%20also%20without%20any%20specific%20instruction.%20In%20fact%20the%20report%20of%20the%20court%20commissioner%20indicates%20that%20at%20most%20of%20the%20entry%20points%20the%20police%20were%20posted%20pursuant%20to%20the%20order%20of%20this%20court%20dated%2023rd%20November.%20There%20is%20a%20serious%20lapse%20on%20the%20authorities%20mentioned%20against%20clauses%201%20-%203.%20We%20therefore%20direct%20the%20Commission%20to%20immediately%20initiate%20action%20in%20terms%20of%20section%2014%20of%20the%20CAQM%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20curbs%20cannot%20be%20downgraded%20below%20GRAP%202%20till%20the%20court%20sees%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20downward%20trend%20of%20AQI%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20direct%20all%20the%20states%20to%20use%20funds%20collected%20as%20labour%20cess%20to%20provide%20subsistence%20to%20construction%20workers%20when%20such%20work%20is%20prohibited%20and%20all%20states%20shall%20comply%20with%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20CAQM%20must%20issued%20directions%20to%20relief%20labourers%20and%20daily%20wagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732534260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frr7oje2_delhi-smog_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-supreme-court-top-court-acts-against-officials-in-delhi-pollution-case-tough-curbs-stay-7101750%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tough%20restrictions%20on%20vehicular%20movement%20and%20construction%20activities%20in%20Delhi%20will%20stay%20for%20now%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-supreme-court-top-court-acts-against-officials-in-delhi-pollution-case-tough-curbs-stay-7101750%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DC%20full%20squad%2C%20IPL%20Auction%3A%20Mitchell%20Starc%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20strengthen%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20core%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732534230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115660493%2Cimgsize-38380.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.co