26quot%3Bmaliciously%20taken%20out%20of%20logical%20context.%26quot%3B%20She%20did%20not%20clarify%20what%20she%20meant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20also%20blasted%20the%20national%20security%20council%2C%20saying%20that%20its%20responsibilities%20related%20to%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20country%2C%20not%20a%20vice%20president's%20remarks%20about%20a%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccb5e436-2f86-4816-9ccf-f78b23e2f828%5C%22%3EA%20partnership%20doomed%20from%20the%20start%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Philippines%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20and%20president%20are%20elected%20separately%20and%20don't%20necessarily%20hail%20from%20the%20same%20party%20or%20ideology%2C%20though%20Duterte%20and%20Marcos%20positioned%20themselves%20as%20running%20mates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20rose%20to%20power%20as%20the%20legacies%20of%20their%20fathers%20loomed%20large%20in%20the%20Philippines.%20Duterte's%20father%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphilippines-president-tells-vaccine-deniers-die-any-time-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERodrigo%20Duterte%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20president%20from%202016%20to%202022%20and%20earned%20himself%20a%20controversial%20%26quot%3Bstrongman%26quot%3B%20reputation%20for%20his%20hardline%20war%20on%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarcos'%20father%2C%20Ferdinand%20Marcos%20Sr.%2C%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-philippines-elected-a-dictators-son-as-president-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edictator%20who%20ruled%20the%20Philippines%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%201965%20to%201986%2C%20enacting%20martial%20law%20in%201972%20to%20extend%20his%20grip%20on%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair's%20families%20forged%20an%20alliance%20in%202022%2C%20uniting%20Duterte's%20base%20in%20the%20south%20and%20Marcos'%20voters%20in%20the%20north%20to%20secure%20a%20general%20election%20victory.%20They%20had%20vowed%20at%20the%20time%20to%20unite%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20out%20of%20convenience%2C%26quot%3B%20Ronald%20Holmes%2C%20who%20teaches%20political%20science%20at%20De%20La%20Salle%20University%20in%20Manila%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20nothing%20between%20them%20in%20the%20past%20that%20would've%20bound%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20partnership%20ruptured%20quickly%20after%20their%20win%2C%20as%20they%20disagreed%20on%20diplomacy%20and%20governance%2C%20like%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20rising%20China.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pna.gov.ph%2Farticles%2F1174279%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20Marcos%20formed%20his%20cabinet%2C%20Duterte%20was%20also%20assigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20instead%20of%20the%20national%20defense%20portfolio%20she%20had%20been%20gunning%20for.%20She%20resigned%20from%20the%20post%20two%20years%20later%2C%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20then%20announced%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsinfo.inquirer.net%2F1994721%2Fcastro-seeks-comprehensive-investigation-into-deped-on-vps-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20into%20her%20department%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20Duterte%20faced%20accusations%20of%20improperly%20using%20funds%20and%20amid%20reports%20that%20students%20were%20faring%20poorly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20overt%20signs%20of%20the%20pair's%20crumbling%20partnership%20emerged%20in%20October%2C%20when%20Duterte%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F10%2F22%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fduterte-marcos-philippines-feud.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20and%20Marcos%20had%20joined%20forces%20as%20running%20mates%20simply%20to%20win%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20she%20had%20recently%20dreamt%20of%20Marcos%20and%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20cut%20his%20head%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e196b6c-d7cf-44c9-92ca-73b1ee11581e%5C%22%3EImpeachment%20may%20prove%20difficult%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20remarks%20on%20Sunday%20were%20more%20than%20references%20to%20dreams%20and%20jokes%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20an%20overt%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20of%20her%20nation's%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20no%20longer%20rhetoric%2C%26quot%3B%20Jorge%20Tigno%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20the%20Philippines%20Diliman%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20threaten%20the%20president%2C%20that's%20no%20longer%20a%20rhetorical%20statement.%20It's%20even%20worse%20when%2C%20afterward%2C%20you%20say%20it's%20not%20a%20joke.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolmes%20said%20the%20likeliest%20course%20of%20action%20from%20the%20central%20government%20would%20be%20an%20impeachment%20attempt%20against%20Duterte%20based%20on%20her%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20endeavor%20may%20prove%20turbulent.%20The%20motion%20must%20pass%20through%20the%20Philippines'%20House%20of%20Representatives%20and%20then%20the%20Senate%2C%20which%20is%20due%20for%20a%20change-up%20in%20the%20coming%202025%20midterm%20elections.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConviction%20in%20the%20Senate%20at%20this%20point%20might%20be%20pretty%20difficult%20because%20you%20have%20about%20a%20third%20of%20the%20Senate%20who%20can%20be%20thought%20of%20as%20allies%20of%20the%20vice%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20Holmes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20impeachment%20fail%2C%20it's%20unclear%20what%20will%20happen%20within%20the%20Marcos%20administration.%20It%20is%20due%20to%20govern%20until%20the%20Philippines'%20next%20election%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETigno%20said%20that%20Duterte%2C%20devoid%20of%20significant%20leadership%20roles%2C%20should%20have%20little%20effect%20on%20Marcos'%20running%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20worries%20that%20the%20elite%20infighting%20will%20catapult%20national%20politics%20into%20further%20toxicity.%20The%20Philippines%2C%20with%20117%20million%20people%2C%20is%20Southeast%20Asia's%20second-most%20populated%20nation%2C%20and%20has%20been%20one%20of%20Washington's%20key%20allies%20as%20the%20US%20seeks%20to%20compete%20against%20China's%20growing%20influence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20could%20end%20up%20with%20what%20they%20have%20now%20in%20the%20US.%20A%20polarized%20system%2C%20a%20polarized%20situation%20between%20the%20Duterte%20and%20the%20Marcos%20camp%2C%26quot%3B%20Tigno%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20a%20'good%20vs%20evil'%20kind%20of%20polarization.%20It's%20more%20of%20one%20elite%20group%20competing%20for%20power%20and%20position%20against%20another%20elite%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespersons%20for%20Duterte%20and%20Marcos%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsara-duterte-assassinate-president-wife-ferdinand-marcos-junior-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732531398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67444a0afa0140cdd565257d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsara-duterte-assassinate-president-wife-ferdinand-marcos-junior-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vice%20President%20Sara%20Duterte%20said%20she%20had%20talked%20to%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20her%20boss%20if%20she%20herself%20were%20to%20be%20killed%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20making%20%26quot%3Bno%20joke.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsara-duterte-assassinate-president-wife-ferdinand-marcos-junior-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%