h%20self-worth%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20fulfillment%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20money.%20How%20they%20teach%20that%20might%20surprise%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22faa92aee-78bd-4f14-8406-39706e3bcaef%5C%22%3ECenti-millionaires%20start%20talking%20about%20money%20early%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20members%20want%20to%20buck%20the%20tradition%20of%20not%20talking%20about%20money.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20concern%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-child-gets-more-stuff-but-not-spoiled-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20sure%20children%20don't%20become%20spoiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20entitled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20teach%20members%20to%20start%20talking%20to%20their%20kids%20in%20elementary%20school.%20Kids%20are%20going%20to%20notice%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-jets-soaring-popularity-pandemic-costing-taxpayers-environment-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20everyone%20is%20traveling%20by%20private%20jet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20kids%20know%20they're%20different%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20point%20trying%20to%20hide%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20members%20try%20to%20create%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20We%20recommend%20members%20talk%20with%20their%20kids%20around%20the%20child's%20birthday%20each%20year%20and%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20you%20bring%20to%20the%20family%20in%20the%20next%20year%3F%20What%20responsibilities%20can%20you%20take%20on%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247c8fa01-ddbf-4d82-b39c-d546e1690022%5C%22%3EEveryone%20is%20paying%20for%20college%2C%20and%20the%20support%20doesn't%20stop%20there%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20for%20all%20college%20expenses%20for%20my%20own%20two%20kids.%20Almost%20all%20our%20members%20do%20the%20same.%20There%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20debate%20around%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20much%20more%20discussion%20about%20when%20to%20stop%20financially%20supporting%20children.%20That's%20very%20personal%20to%20each%20family%2C%20but%20most%20centimillionaires%20are%20giving%20their%20children%20some%20financial%20support%20well%20into%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20families%2C%20that%20continues%20throughout%20the%20lifetime.%20One%20member%20has%20a%20child%20who%20works%20in%20healthcare.%20That%20woman%20doesn't%20make%20much%20money%2C%20but%20she%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20fulfillment%2C%20so%20her%20parents%20are%20happy%20to%20keep%20supporting%20her%20financially.%20That%20member%20also%20plans%20to%20leave%20more%20to%20the%20daughter%20working%20in%20healthcare%20than%20they'll%20leave%20to%20their%20children%20with%20more%20lucrative%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22478fa8e3-7571-4295-a152-4a3ba1f87da7%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20about%20values%2C%20and%20politics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20our%20members%20are%20philanthropists%2C%20and%20they%20need%20to%20talk%20openly%20with%20their%20kids%20about%20their%20values%20and%20the%20causes%20they%20support.%20They%20don't%20want%20to%20hand%20over%20their%20wealth%20to%20their%20kids%20and%20have%20money%20go%20toward%20causes%20they%20don't%20support.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20their%20kids%20to%20have%20to%20follow%20a%20wealth%20management%20plan%20that%20they%20ethically%20don't%20agree%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20to%20lots%20of%20interesting%20conversations.%20Most%20often%2C%20it's%20around%20politics.%20Children%20want%20to%20be%20heard%2C%20and%20the%20parents%20need%20to%20hear%20them.%20Most%20families%20are%20able%20to%20negotiate%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca0ac4a8-1dde-4bcb-83cf-1d3f9f63ac27%5C%22%3ECentimillionaires%20learn%20from%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20one%20of%20our%20older%20members%20was%20frustrated%20that%20his%20son%20didn't%20want%20to%20get%20a%20prenuptial%20agreement%20with%20his%20bride-to-be.%20He%20felt%20s