er%20in%20Florida%2C%20then%20as%20part%20of%20the%20president-elect's%20transition%20team.%20By%20leveraging%20his%20access%20to%20Trump%2C%20Ballard%20Partners%20was%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20old%20white-shoe%20lobbying%20firms%20that%20have%20been%20the%20industry's%20dominant%20players%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20first%20year%20of%20Trump's%20term%2C%20Ballard%20added%20dozens%20of%20major%20clients%2C%20including%20Google%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Uber%2C%20American%20Airlines%2C%20Honda%2C%20the%20tobacco%20giant%20Reynolds%20American%2C%20the%20private-prison%20firm%20Geo%20Group%2C%20and%20the%20American%20Health%20Care%20Association.%20By%202020%2C%20Ballard%20ranked%20as%20the%20nation's%20seventh-largest%20federal%20lobbying%20firm%20in%20terms%20of%20income%20%E2%80%94%20an%20astounding%20feat%20for%20an%20office%20that%20was%20only%203%20years%20old.%20Ballard's%20lobbying%20business%20in%20Florida%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20regularly%20ranks%20among%20the%20state's%20top-earning%20firms%2C%20making%20it%20ideally%20positioned%20to%20once%20again%20be%20the%20go-to%20lobbying%20shop%20for%20corporations%20and%20special%20interests%20eager%20to%20cozy%20up%20to%20Trump%20and%20his%20MAGA%20allies%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorporate%20clients%20need%20lobbyists%20who%20appreciate%20that%20Trump%20is%20%26quot%3Bdisrupting%20the%20status%20quo%20in%20Washington%2C%26quot%3B%20Sayfie%2C%20the%20Ballard%20lobbyist%2C%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20creates%20a%20sense%20of%20both%20possibility%20%E2%80%94%20and%20great%20worry%20and%20anxiety%20to%20navigate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20presidential%20transition%20poses%20significant%20challenges%20for%20corporations.%20Business%20thrives%20on%20stability%3B%20it's%20hard%20to%20make%20plans%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20all%20the%20uncertainty%20that%20comes%20from%20shifting%20political%20philosophies%2C%20legislative%20goals%2C%20and%20regulatory%20ambitions.%20But%20lobbying%20insiders%20say%20Trump's%20presidential%20transition%20has%20brought%20a%20new%20level%20of%20unpredictability%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20also%20represents%20a%20golden%20opportunity%2C%20for%20those%20able%20to%20capitalize%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20has%20a%20mandate%20from%20the%20American%20people%20and%20is%20using%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20B.%20Jeffrey%20Brooks%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Adams%20and%20Reese%2C%20a%20law%20firm%20with%20more%20than%20300%20attorneys%20and%20lobbyists%20across%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BIt%20hasn't%20been%20this%20exciting%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20since%201994%2C%20when%20Republicans%20had%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frollcall.com%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2Fthe-contract-with-americas-legacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EContract%20with%20America%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20appointments%20and%20his%20campaign%20promises%2C%20lobbyists%20say%2C%20Trump%20has%20clearly%20signaled%20his%20desire%20to%20remake%20Washington%20in%20Florida's%20regulation-slashing%2C%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B-fighting%20image%20%E2%80%94%20and%20do%20so%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20his%20%26quot%3BWinter%20White%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20now%20a%20political%20redoubt%20for%20all%20seasons.%20Already%2C%20many%20of%20the%20top%20slots%20in%20Trump's%20administration%20are%20going%20to%20Floridians%20who%20have%20stuck%20by%20him%20through%20his%20many%20legal%20and%20political%20troubles.%20Among%20them%20are%20two%20former%20Ballard%20lobbyists%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-susie-wiles-florida-bill-stepien-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESusie%20Wiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whom%20Trump%20has%20tapped%20to%20serve%20as%20his%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nominates-pam-bondi-attorney-general-matt-gaetz-withdrew-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Pam%20B