eans%20that%20betting%20on%20the%20broader%20market%20and%20momentum%20is%20probably%20not%20the%20best%20strategy%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20the%20investment%20bank%20suggests%20seeking%20alpha%2C%20a%20short%20way%20of%20saying%20returns%20above%20the%20broad%20market.%20The%20way%20through%20is%20by%20focusing%20on%20four%20key%20areas%20that%20include%20opportunities%20from%20a%20broadening%20out%20of%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20hunting%20for%20value%2C%20adding%20foreign%20stocks%2C%20and%20considering%20companies%20engaged%20in%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFour%20areas%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20interest%20rates%20rose%20at%20the%20fastest%20pace%20in%20four%20decades%2C%20companies%20that%20relied%20on%20debt%20or%20had%20weaker%20balance%20sheets%20fell%20behind%20their%20larger%20counterparts%20that%20had%20stronger%20balance%20sheets%20to%20rely%20on.%20But%20as%20the%20rate%20cuts%20from%20this%20cycle%20take%20effect%2C%20smaller%20companies%20will%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBelow%20is%20a%20chart%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%20that%20shows%20how%20the%20major%20indexes%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20global%20firms%2C%20performed%20against%20the%20broader%20market%20since%20the%20first%20Fed%20hike%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221270%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Equity%20performance%20during%20rate%20hikes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740fa85fa0140cdd5650ac1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20note%20recommends%20rotating%20as%20rates%20create%20a%20more%20favorable%20environment%20for%20smaller%20cap%20companies%20by%20%3Cstrong%3Eshifting%20aw