pan%3EAs%20for%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20while%20they%20may%20not%20be%20as%20attractive%2C%20some%20opportunities%20could%20be%20found%20within%20specific%20companies.%20For%20Europe%2C%20companies%20not%20reliant%20on%20exports%2C%20such%20as%20telecommunications%20and%20real-estate%20firms%2C%20or%20those%20where%20half%20their%20revenues%20are%20earned%20within%20the%20US%20market%20but%20are%20cheaper%20than%20their%20American%20counterparts%2C%20are%20a%20good%20bet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinally%2C%20capital%20markets%20activity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20an%20uptick.%20That%20said%2C%20Goldman%20suggests%20looking%20for%20names%20involved%20in%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-strategies-beat-the-stock-market-in-2025-goldman-sachs-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732528801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740fb3eede4eeae3929253f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-strategies-beat-the-stock-market-in-2025-goldman-sachs-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20focusing%20on%20these%20areas%20of%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20investors%20can%20beat%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20next%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmaidan%40businessinsider.com%20(Laila%20Maidan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-strategies-beat-the-stock-market-in-2025-goldman-sachs-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Charli%20XCX%20Bringing%20%E2%80%98Party%20Girl%E2%80%99%20Lineup%20to%20London%E2%80%99s%20Lido%20Festival%20in%20Summer%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732528800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%