om%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fglobal%2Flana-del-rey-uk-ireland-tour-dates-wembley-stadium-1236222449%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2216th%20Century%20Mosque%2C%20A%20City%20On%20Fire%3A%20Sambhal%20Violence%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%2030%20years%20since%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20another%20mosque%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20finds%20itself%20at%20the%20epicentre%20of%20a%20contentious%20debate.%20A%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20the%2016th-century%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20a%20Mughal-era%20mosque%2C%20in%20Moradabad's%20Sambhal%2C%20led%20to%20multiple%20deaths%2C%20arrests%20and%20a%20riot%20that%20brought%20the%20city%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsambhal-violence-2-dead-vehicles-on-fire-violence-in-ups-sambhal-over-mosque-survey-7094518%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJama%20Masjid%20in%20Sambhal%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20built%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20first%20Mughal%20emperor%2C%20Babur%2C%20between%201526%20and%201530%2C%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20major%20mosques%20constructed%20during%20his%20brief%20but%20impactful%20rule.%20The%20other%20two%20are%20the%20mosque%20at%20Panipat%20and%20the%20now-demolished%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20historical%20reports%2C%20the%20mosque's%20construction%20was%20supervised%20by%20Hindu%20Beg%20Qucin%2C%20one%20of%20Babur's%20trusted%20lieutenants%2C%20in%20December%201526.%20Its%20architectural%20style%20mirrors%20the%20era's%20evolving%20Mughal%20design%2C%20featuring%20a%20large%20square%20hall%20with%20a%20central%20dome.%20Persian%20inscriptions%20within%20the%20mosque%20confirm%20its%20Mughal%20origins%2C%20though%20some%20historians%20claim%20remnants%20of%20pre-existing%20Hindu%20temples%20were%20integrated%20into%20its%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESambhal%20itself%20holds%20religious%20significance%20for%20Hindus%2C%20as%20the%20purported%20birthplace%20of%20Kalki%2C%20the%20tenth%20and%20final%20avatar%20of%20Vishnu.%20According%20to%20Hindu%20scriptures%2C%20Kalki%20is%20destined%20to%20appear%20in%20Sambhal%20to%20end%20the%20Kalyug%20(age%20of%20darkness).%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20grand%20Kalki%20Dham%2C%20calling%20for%20%26quot%3BRam%20Rashtra%26quot%3B%20and%20claiming%20that%20%26quot%3BKalki's%20avatar%20will%20determine%20the%20course%20of%20thousands%20of%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESambhal's%20spiritual%20history%20-%20with%20different%20faiths%20overlapping%20each%20other%20in%20history%20-%20forms%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20current%20legal%20and%20ideological%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Legal%20Dispute%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20Sambhal%20by%20advocate%20Vishnu%20Shanker%20Jain%20and%20others.%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20also%20known%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20and%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20disputes%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20was%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20temple%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Kalki.%20The%20petition%20alleged%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20constructed%20after%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20during%20Babur's%20invasion%20in%201526-27.%20The%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20historical%20texts%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBaburnamah%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAin-e-Akbari%26quot%3B%20document%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Babur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20claims%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20built%20by%20the%20Hindu%20mythological%20figure%20Vishwakarma%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20universe.%20Babur's%20forces%20allegedly%20destroyed%20the%20temple%20partially%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20mosque%20to%20establish%20Islamic%20supremacy.%20The%20petition%20further%20criticises%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20site%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20protected%20monument%20under%20the%20Ancient%20Monuments%20and%20Archaeological%20Sites%20and%20Remains%20Act%2C%201958.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20demand%20unrestricted%20access%20to%20the%20mosque%20for%20Hindus%2C%20claiming%20their%20right%20to%20worship%20was%20being%20unlawfully%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Survey%20And%20Its%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20court%20ordered%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20mosque%20on%20November%2019%2C%202024.%20Advocate%20Commissioner%20Ramesh%20Raghav%2C%20along%20with%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20police%2C%20carried%20out%20the%20survey%20the%20same%20day.%20This%20rapid%20action%20drew%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters%2C%20with%20claims%20of%20judicial%20overreach%20and%20procedural%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20community%2C%20including%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20management%20committee%2C%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20survey.%20They%20pointed%20to%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%201991%2C%20which%20prohibits%20altering%20the%20status%20of%20any%20religious%20site%20as%20it%20existed%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%20Ziaur%20Rehman%20Barq%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20from%20Sambhal%2C%20condemned%20the%20move%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2024%20tensions%20boiled%20over%20as%20a%20second%20survey%20was%20scheduled.%20Protests%20erupted%20near%20the%20mosque%20as%20hundreds%20of%20locals%2C%20fearing%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%2C%20gathered%20to%20resist%20the%20survey.%20The%20demonstrations%20quickly%20turned%20violent%2C%20with%20protesters%20throwing%20stones%20and%20setting%20vehicles%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20personnel%20responded%20with%20tear%20gas%20and%20baton%20charges%20to%20control%20the%20mob.%20Four%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20over%2030%20police%20personnel%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20vehicles%20were%20torched%2C%20and%20property%20around%20the%20mosque%20was%20damaged.%20Internet%20services%20were%20suspended%2C%20prohibitory%20orders%20were%20imposed%2C%20and%20schools%20were%20shut%20for%20a%20day%20to%20prevent%20further%20escalation.%20The%20Moradabad%20Police%20said%20that%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20violence%20would%20face%20stringent%20legal%20action%2C%20including%20charges%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20(NSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Vishnu%20Shanker%20Jain%20stated%20that%20the%20ASI%20must%20take%20control%20of%20the%20site%20to%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20its%20origins.%20Ziaur%20Rehman%20Barq%20urged%20the%20community%20to%20remain%20calm%20while%20challenging%20the%20survey%20legally.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Mayawati%20criticised%20the%20government's%20inaction%20in%20preventing%20communal%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20argue%20that%20allowing%20such%20cases%20undermines%20the%20The%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20maintain%20the%20religious%20status%20quo%20post-Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732528560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ff8q0l81o_sambhal-mosque-violence-explained-_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsambhal-mosque-jama-masjid-up-violence-16th-century-mosque-a-city-on-fire-sambhal-violence-explained-7100779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sambhal%20Violence%3A%20Over%2030%20years%20since%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20another%20mosque%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20finds%20itself%20at%20the%20epicentre%20of%20a%20contentious%20debate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C