a%20rapidly%20shifting%20world%20order%2C%20and%20to%20present%20himself%20as%20both%20globally%20engaged%20and%20strategically%20patient.%20When%20Biden%20asked%20MBS%20to%20ease%20oil%20prices%2C%20he%20declined.%20American%20diplomats%20were%20shocked%2C%20but%20MBS%20needed%20oil%20revenues%20to%20keep%20flowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-look-at-saudi-crown-prince-mohammed-bin-salmans-rise-to-power-6384434%5C%22%3EMBS's%20rise%20to%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20marked%20by%20extravagant%20spending%2C%20bold%20cultural%20reforms%20and%20a%20devastating%20war%20in%20Yemen.%20The%20cocksure%20young%20prince%20had%20shaken%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20its%20foundations.%20But%20the%202022%20meeting%20with%20Biden%20showed%20that%20MBS%2C%20while%20no%20less%20ambitious%2C%20was%20increasingly%20attuned%20to%20his%20place%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20Reforms%20that%20had%20once%20generated%20headlines%20%E2%80%94%20women%20driving%2C%20genders%20mixing%20in%20public%2C%20entertainment%20events%20%E2%80%94%20have%20become%20the%20new%20normal.%20New%20industries%20are%20taking%20root%20across%20the%20country%20and%20a%20brand%20new%20megacity%2C%20NEOM%2C%20is%20under%20construction.%20MBS%20has%20played%20the%20role%20of%20peacemaker%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20even%20forged%20a%20closer%20relationship%20with%20Turkey's%20Tayyip%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%2C%20whose%20intelligence%20services%20leaked%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20Khashoggi%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20older%2C%20evolved%20MBS%20may%20be%20further%20emboldened%20by%20the%20looming%20change%20in%20Washington.%20During%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20the%20crown%20prince%20maintained%20close%20ties%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20With%20Trump's%20return%2C%20MBS's%20standing%20in%20the%20international%20arena%20will%20surely%20be%20solidified.%20His%20cultivation%20of%20Trump%20and%20his%20inner%20circle%2C%20once%20seen%20as%20a%20risky%20bet%20on%20an%20unconventional%20president%2C%20has%20proven%20prescient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20how%20MBS%20has%20developed%20his%20style%20of%20leadership%2C%20it's%20worth%20considering%20both%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Khashoggi's%20murder%20as%20well%20as%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20changes%20MBS%20is%20bringing%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20through%20his%202030%20Vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMBS%20took%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20responsibility%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%202018%20killing%20inside%20the%20Saudi%20consulate%20Istanbul%2C%20although%20he%20also%20denied%20ordering%20it.%20The%20gruesome%20details%20that%20emerged%20gave%20him%20little%20choice%20but%20to%20pivot%20inward%20and%20focus%20on%20creating%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20For%20that%2C%20MBS%20needed%20money.%20He%20took%20the%20controversial%20view%20that%20the%20country's%20future%20depends%20in%20large%20part%20on%20monetizing%20its%20oil%20today%20before%20demand%20begins%20to%20peter%20out.%20The%202019%20IPO%20of%20Saudi%20Aramco%20%E2%80%94%20considered%20the%20crown%20jewel%20of%20the%20country's%20energy%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20was%20one%20way%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%20Although%20the%20share%20sale%20fell%20short%20of%20an%20initial%20%242%20trillion%20valuation%20target%2C%20the%20process%20still%20raised%20%2425.6%20billion%2C%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20IPO%20in%20history%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMBS%20has%20been%20using%20some%20of%20that%20money%20to%20rebrand%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20a%20major%20destination%20for%20international%20travelers.%20New%20hotels%20are%20opening%20and%20being%20constructed%20all%20along%20the%20coast%20in%20the%20hopes%20that%20millions%20of%20tourists%20can%20be%20diverted%20from%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20Gulf%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20From%20Formula%201%20races%20in%20Jeddah%20to%20the%20MDLBeast%20Soundstorm%20music%20festival%20attracting%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20attendees%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20rebranding%20itself%20as%20a%20major%20destination.%20The%20rebuild%20also%20extends%20to%20a%20giant%20400-meter%20cubic%20structure%20under%20construction%20in%20Riyadh%20that%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20buildings%2C%20including%20100%2C000%20residential%20units%2C%209%2C000%20hotel%20rooms%2C%2080%20entertainment%20and%20cultural%20venues%20and%201.4%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20Saudis%2C%20especially%20the%20youth%20who%20make%20up%2070%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20these%20changes%20represent%20unprecedented%20opportunities.%20The%20burgeoning%20entertainment%20and%20tourism%20sectors%20are%20creating%20thousands%20of%20jobs%2C%20and%20young%20Saudis%20are%20embracing%20new%20freedoms%20in%20music%2C%20art%20and%20social%20interactions.%20The%20ancient%20city%20of%20Al-Ula%2C%20with%20its%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%20Hegra%2C%20has%20become%20a%20centerpiece%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20tourism%20push.%20The%20Winter%20at%20Tantora%20festival%2C%20launched%20in%202018%2C%20brings%20international%20artists%20and%20visitors%20to%20the%20region%2C%20showcasing%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20pre-Islamic%20history%20and%20natural%20beauty.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20kingdom%20introduced%20a%20new%20visa%20system%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20tourists%20from%2049%20countries%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENEOM%2C%20the%20%24500%20billion%20megacity%20project%20announced%20to%20skepticism%20in%202017%2C%20is%20taking%20shape%20because%20of%20the%20sheer%20willpower%20of%20MBS%20alone.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20project%20the%20market%20asked%20for%2C%20but%20in%20his%20eyes%20it%20is%20a%20crucial%20development%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country.%20Nestled%20in%20the%20northwestern%20corner%20of%20the%20country%2C%20a%20largely%20undeveloped%20region%20near%20Jordan%2C%20Egypt%20and%20Israel%2C%20MBS%20is%20betting%20that%20by%20conjuring%20a%20huge%20city%20of%20the%20future%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20will%20ensure%20its%20relevance%20for%20decades%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20steel%20shipments%20coming%20from%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20construction%20on%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Line%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20170%20kilometer-long%20linear%20city%20within%20the%20NEOM%20project%2C%20is%20underway.%20The%20design%20embodies%20MBS's%20approach%20to%20development.%20The%20project%20seems%20impossible%2C%20perhaps%20unfeasible%2C%20yet%20it%20is%20happening%20nonetheless.%20There%20have%20been%20setbacks%2C%20delays%20and%20budget%20cuts.%20Some%20targets%20have%20been%20significantly%20pared%20back.%20The%20CEO%20of%20NEOM%20was%20also%20replaced%20earlier%20this%20month.%20But%20this%20incredibly%20ambitious%20project%20keeps%20moving%20ahead%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emerging%20challenge%20is%20finding%20enough%20cash%20to%20complete%20so%20many%20mega%20projects%20and%20make%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20economy%20sustainable.%20The%20country%20is%20on%20a%20cost-cutting%20and%20efficiency%20mission%20that%20includes%20paying%20some%20big%20vendors%20late%20to%20preserve%20cash.%20No%20matter%20how%20fast%20Saudi%20Arabia%20monetizes%20its%20oil%2C%20it%20also%20needs%20others%20to%20believe%20in%20the%20story%20and%20invest%2C%20too.%20That%20isn't%20happening%20fast%20enough%20and%20remains%20an%20existential%20risk%20to%20the%20MBS%20project%20over%20the%20next%20six%20years.%20MBS%20is%20betting%20a%20lot%20on%20uncertainty%3A%20If%20he%20builds%20it%2C%20will%20anyone%20come%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategic%20Thinking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20center%20of%20all%20the%20biggest%20initiatives%20is%20the%20country's%20sovereign%20Public%20Investment%20Fund%2C%20which%20became%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20aggressive%20financial%20players%20under%20MBS's%20direction.%20By%202022%2C%20its%20assets%20under%20management%20had%20grown%20to%20more%20than%20%24600%20billion%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20reach%20%242%20trillion%20by%202030.%20The%20PIF's%20investments%20range%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20startups%20to%20Premier%20League%20football%20clubs.%20In%202021%2C%20it%20acquired%20the%20football%20team%20Newcastle%20United.%20The%202022%20launch%20of%20LIV%20Golf%2C%20a%20PIF-backed%20challenger%20to%20the%20established%20PGA%20Tour%2C%20epitomized%20the%20PIF's%20standard%20approach%3A%20big%2C%20bold%20and%20unafraid%20to%20ruffle%20feathers%20in%20pursuit%20of%20Saudi%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20critics%20labeled%20these%20investments%20as%20%E2%80%9Csportswashing%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20using%20sports%20to%20improve%20Saudi's%20international%20image%20and%20distract%20from%20ongoing%20human%20rights%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20MBS%20sees%20them%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20strategy.%20The%202034%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20bid%2C%20jointly%20submitted%20with%20Egypt%2C%20and%20the%20hosting%20of%20the%202030%20World%20Expo%20aren't%20just%20about%20image%20rehabilitation%3B%20they%20are%20calculated%20moves%20to%20position%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20a%20global%20entertainment%20and%20sports%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20powerful%20symbol%20of%20Saudi's%20financial%20clout%20is%20the%20annual%20Future%20Investment%20Initiative%20(FII)%20forum%2C%20dubbed%20%E2%80%9CDavos%20in%20the%20Desert.%E2%80%9D%20Many%20Western%20organizations%20initially%20boycotted%20the%20conference%20following%20the%20Khashoggi%20killing.%20But%20in%20October%202024%2C%20the%20forum%20drew%20its%20largest%20crowd%20ever%2C%20with%20global%20CEOs%2C%20tech%20leaders%20and%20politicians%20coming%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20persuading%20PIF%20and%20MBS's%20advisers%20to%20give%20them%20access%20to%20its%20once-in-a-generation%20spending%20spree.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20very%2C%20very%20excited%20and%20happy%20with%20what%20we%20have%20achieved%20in%20the%20Saudi%20Vision%202030%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20complacent%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammed%20al%20Jadaan%2C%20Saudi's%20finance%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20doubling%20down%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20we%20are%20doing%20the%20right%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FII%20demonstrates%20that%20instead%20of%20direct%20confrontation%2C%20MBS%20has%20learned%20to%20wield%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20economic%20and%20cultural%20clout%20more%20strategically.%20When%20faced%20with%20international%20criticism%2C%20the%20kingdom%20increasingly%20applies%20pressure%20through%20business%20deals%20and%20visa%20policies%20rather%20than%20public%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20clout%20is%20impacting%20geopolitics%20as%20well.%20At%20a%20summit%20in%20Al-Ula%20in%20January%202021%2C%20MBS%20personally%20brokered%20an%20end%20to%20a%20rift%20between%20several%20Gulf%20States%20and%20Qatar%20over%20the%20latter's%20foreign%20policy%20and%20its%20media's%20role%20in%20fomenting%20regional%20differences.%20The%20Crown%20Prince%20also%20symbolically%20embraced%20Qatar's%20emir%20in%20a%20public%20gesture%20of%20reconciliation.%20This%20move%20stabilized%20the%20region%20and%20allowed%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20present%20a%20more%20united%20Gulf%20front%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20even%20as%20MBS's%20long-time%20partner%2C%20Mohammed%20bin%20Zayed%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20appeared%20to%20struggle%20to%20embrace%20the%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20remarkably%2C%20MBS%20has%20opened%20backchannel%20negotiations%20with%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20long-standing%20nemesis.%20These%20talks%2C%20mediated%20by%20Iraq%20and%20Oman%2C%20marked%20a%20dramatic%20shift%20from%20the%20confrontational%20stance%20of%20MBS's%20early%20years%20in%20power%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20in%20Yemen%2C%20where%20a%20Saudi-led%20coalition%20has%20been%20fighting%20Iranian-backed%20Houthi%20rebels%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaudi%20First%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20critically%2C%20none%20of%20these%20efforts%20were%20done%20in%20lockstep%20with%20the%20US.%20Saudi%20foreign%20policy%20is%20now%20definitively%20%E2%80%9CSaudi%20first.%E2%80%9D%20And%20domestically%2C%20MBS%20has%20maintained%20a%20firm%20grip%20on%20power.%20Rivals%20within%20the%20royal%20family%20remain%20sidelined%20or%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20seemingly%20for%20life.%20Activists%20and%20critics%20continue%20to%20face%20harsh%20punishments%2C%20though%20with%20less%20of%20the%20brazen%20impunity%20that%20characterized%20the%20Khashoggi%20affair.%20The%20release%20of%20women's%20rights%20activist%20Loujain%20al-Hathloul%20in%20February%202021%2C%20while%20celebrated%20internationally%2C%20came%20with%20strict%20conditions%20including%20a%20travel%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20rights%20organizations%20continue%20to%20criticize%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20treatment%20of%20dissidents%20and%20its%20lack%20of%20political%20freedoms%2C%20but%20the%20world%20that%20sought%20to%20isolate%20MBS%20now%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20engage.%20The%20age%20of%20MBS%20has%20begun%20%E2%80%94%20an%20era%20where%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20influence%20extends%20far%20beyond%20oil%20markets.%20From%20Silicon%20Valley%20boardrooms%20to%20Premier%20League%20stadiums%20and%20gaming%2C%20from%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20to%20artificial%20intelligence%20research%2C%20the%20kingdom's%20fingerprints%20are%20increasingly%20visible%20on%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Saudi%20Arabia%20prepares%20to%20host%20the%20World%20Expo%20in%202030%20and%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%202034%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20MBS%20has%20transformed%20his%20nation.%20His%20model%20of%20authoritarian%20modernization%2C%20combining%20social%20reforms%20with%20strict%20political%20control%2C%20has%20also%20inspired%20other%20leaders%20in%20the%20region%20and%20beyond.%20Whether%20this%20new%20paradigm%20proves%20sustainable%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20is%20certain%3A%20The%20implications%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20transformation%20under%20MBS%20will%20reverberate%20far%20beyond%20the%20kingdom's%20borders%20for%20decades%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBradley%20Hope%20is%20the%20co-author%20of%20Billion%20Dollar%20Whale%20and%20Blood%20and%20Oil%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20author%20of%20The%20Rebel%20and%20the%20Kingdom.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Project%20Brazen%2C%20a%20journalism%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732528140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Ftfq4l00o_mohammed-bin-salman-reuters_625x300_20_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-age-of-mbs-has-begun-saudi-princes-influence-on-economy-beyond-oil-7101378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20bin%20Salman's%20rise%20to%20power%20had%20been%20marked%20by%20extravagant%20spending%2C%20bold%20cultural%20reforms%20and%20a%20devastating%20war%20in%20Yemen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-age-of-mbs-has-begun-saudi-princes-influence-on-economy-beyond-oil-7101378%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22E.coli%2C%20a%20global%20epidemic%3F%20Things%20we%20urgently%20need%20to%20know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732527952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115656718%2Cimgsize-853749.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fe-coli-a-global-epidemic-things-we-urgently-need-to-know-about-the-bacterial-infection%2Farticleshow%2F115656758.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22E.%20coli%20outbreaks%20linked%20to%20contaminated%20food%20like%20carrots%20and%20onions%20have%20raised%20concerns.%20While%20most%20E.%20coli%20st