%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20influencing%20or%20something%20conceptually%20interesting.%20But%20when%20I%20looked%20a%20little%20further%20into%20one%20of%20the%20AI-generated%20influencer%20accounts%20on%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20had%20reportedly%20gotten%20some%20brand%20deals%20%E2%80%94%20I%20found%20a%20different%20type%20of%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20AI%20influencers%20had%20a%20link%20in%20her%20bio%20to%20a%20profile%20on%20Fanvue%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-onlyfans-content-platform-explained-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOnlyFans%3C%2Fa%3E%20competitor.%20On%20her%20Fanvue%20account%2C%20the%20influencer%20posted%20proactive%20photos%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20a%20%247-a-month%20subscription%2C%20I%20could%20see%20her%20nude%20photos.%20(I%20feel%20strange%20saying%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eshe%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Enude%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20because%20this%20person%20doesn't%20exist.%20Remember%3A%20She's%20AI.%20But%20this%20is%20where%20we%20are%20in%202024%2C%20I%20suppose.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAh%2C%20so%20I%20get%20it%20now%3A%20The%20business%20was%20always%20pornography%20%E2%80%94%20Instagram%20and%20other%20social%20media%20were%20just%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20conversion%20funnel.%20These%20accounts%20weren't%20trying%20to%20become%20%26quot%3BInstagram%20influencers%26quot%3B%20who%20made%20money%20through%20promoting%20shampoo%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20using%20Instagram%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-influencer-kimochii-creator-monetization-content-interacting-with-followers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrive%20traffic%20to%20Fanvue%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20they%20could%20get%20men%20to%20pay%20to%20see%20their%20nude%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20potential%20customers%20get%20to%20the%20paysites%2C%20they%20encounter%20more%20AI-generated%20pictures%20and%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20news%20site%20404%20Media%20just%20published%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20this%20world%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.404media.co%2Finside-the-booming-ai-pimping-industry-3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20Booming%20'AI%20Pimping'%20Industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20What%20reporters%20found%20was%20an%20astounding%20amount%20of%20AI-fueled%20accounts%20on%20both%20OnlyFans%20and%20Fanvue.%20Disturbingly%2C%20404%20Media%20found%20a%20number%20of%20these%20accounts%20used%20images%20that%20weren't%20purely%20dreamed%20up%20by%20AI.%20Some%20were%20deepfakes%20%E2%80%94%20fake%20images%20of%20real%20people%20%E2%80%94%20or%20were%20face%20swaps%2C%20using%20someone's%20face%20on%20an%20AI-generated%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20whole%20side%20economy%20of%20people%20selling%20guides%20and%20courses%20on%20how%20others%20can%20set%20up%20their%20own%20businesses%20to%20create%20AI%20models.%20One%20person%20is%20selling%20a%20course%20for%20%24220%20on%20how%20to%20make%20money%20with%20AI%20adult%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fanvue%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20using%20images%20that%20steal%20someone's%20identity%20is%20against%20its%20rules.%20Fanvue%20also%20uses%20a%20third-party%20moderation%20tool%20and%20has%20human%20moderators.%20The%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bdeepfakes%20are%20an%20industry%20challenge.%26quot%3B%20OnlyFans'%20terms%20of%20service%20prohibit%20models%20from%20using%20AI%20chatbots.%20Those%20terms%20also%20say%20that%20AI%20content%20is%20allowed%20only%20if%20users%20can%20tell%20it's%20AI%20and%20only%20if%20that%20content%20features%20the%20verified%20creator%20%E2%80%94%20not%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPotentially%20stolen%20images%20aside%2C%20the%20existence%20of%20AI%20adult%20content%20is%20somewhat%20fraught.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20some%20of%20these%20AI%20creators%20claim%20that%20this