ionship%20with%20President%20Trump%2C%20his%20team%2C%20and%20also%20with%20the%20new%20Congress%20to%20strengthen%20our%20national%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Pentagon%20spokesperson%20also%20told%20the%20outlet%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20combat-capable%20aircraft%20in%20operation%20today%20and%20they%20perform%20exceptionally%20well%20against%20the%20threat%20for%20which%20they%20were%20designed.%20Pilots%20continually%20emphasize%20that%20this%20is%20the%20fighter%20they%20want%20to%20take%20to%20war%20if%20called%20upon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20there%20will%20be%20700%20F-35s%20in%20Europe%20and%20only%2060%20of%20these%20will%20belong%20to%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-f35-idiots-building-unmanned-jets-drone-warfare-doge-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732525847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674436489f2901eb603695fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-f35-idiots-building-unmanned-jets-drone-warfare-doge-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Musk%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20advise%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20government%20efficiency%2C%20has%20said%20before%20that%20the%20F-35%20program%20would%20lose%20to%20a%20drone%20fighter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-f35-idiots-building-unmanned-jets-drone-warfare-doge-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22K-Pop%E2%80%99s%20CD%20Problem%3A%20Environmental%20Groups%20Sound%20Alarm%20on%20Industry%E2%80%99s%20Carbon%20Footprint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732525616000%2