20and%20allies%20to%20analyse%20the%20reasons%20clinically%20and%20undertake%20course%20correction%20in%20five%20months%20to%20coast%20home%20as%20victors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20results%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20which%20went%20to%20polls%20along%20with%20Maharashtra%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20government%2C%20gave%20the%20I.N.D.I.%20Alliance%20some%20breathing%20space.%20Yet%20the%20sheer%20scale%20of%20Mahayuti's%20victory%20relegated%20the%20Jharkhand%20triumph%2C%20recorded%20by%20the%20JMM-Congress%20plus%20alliance%2C%20to%20the%20back%20burner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20this%20massive%20victory%2C%20the%20BJP%20emerged%20stronger.%20The%20inability%20to%20secure%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20now%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20The%20BJP%20leadership%2C%20which%20has%20shown%20its%20resolve%20to%20run%20a%20tight%20ship%2C%20remains%20undiminished%20and%20will%20no%20longer%20feel%20compelled%20to%20consider%20trimming%20its%20sails%20while%20moving%20forward%20at%20full%20steam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20outcome%20will%20be%20felt%20immediately%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20Parliament.%20The%20government%20will%20push%20ahead%20with%20its%20legislative%20agenda%2C%20particularly%20the%20controversial%20Waqf%20Bill%2C%20weathering%20fierce%20opposition%20and%20discomfort%20from%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20unequivocal%20reference%20to%20the%20law%20and%20its%20anachronistic%20existence%20on%20Saturday%20should%20dispel%20any%20doubts%20about%20the%20approach%20to%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20following%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20necessary%20parliamentary%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Select%20Committee%20examining%20the%20Bill%20has%20time%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20week%20of%20the%20session%20to%20submit%20its%20report.%20Once%20the%20report%20on%20the%20Bill%20is%20presented%20to%20the%20Houses%2C%20the%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20list%20of%20businesses%20for%20Parliament%20to%20consider%20and%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changed%20political%20atmosphere%20would%20blunt%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20opposition.%20Its%20passage%20will%20be%20testing%20the%20waters%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20bring%20forward%20the%20last%20and%20third%20issue%20of%20its%20core%20agenda%20-%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20Bill%2C%20which%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20put%20on%20the%20business%20is%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election.%20This%20action%20based%20on%20the%20report%20of%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20is%20bound%20to%20face%20stiff%20opposition%20and%20strong%20views%20from%20either%20side%20of%20the%20aisle.%20Adding%20to%20the%20debate%20would%20be%20the%20arguments%20on%20the%20technicalities%20involved%20in%20enacting%20this%20major%20constitutional%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20session%20between%20November%2025%20and%20December%2020%20would%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20the%20governing%20coalition%20and%20the%20Opposition%20to%20fiercely%20contest%20each%20other's%20ideas.%20From%20now%20on%2C%20the%20bench%20strength%20of%20the%20Opposition%20gets%20a%20boost%20with%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20joining%20the%20ranks%20adding%20vigour%20to%20the%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra's%20outcome%20allows%20the%20BJP%20to%20push%20forward%20with%20its%20core%20Hindutva%20agenda%20with%20renewed%20vigour.%20The%20'Batenge%20to%20Katenge'%20slogan%2C%20popularized%20by%20UP%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20has%20become%20a%20template%2C%20leaving%20little%20to%20the%20imagination%20regarding%20the%20plan%20to%20consolidate%20the%20majority%20vote.%20Meanwhile%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20focused%20on%20spreading%20the%20'Ek%20Hain%20to%20Safe%20Hain'%20message%2C%20with%20scores%20of%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20karyakartas%20knocking%20on%20every%20door%20to%20drive%20the%20point%20home.%20This%20aggressive%20campaign%20could%20become%20the%20standard%20approach%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decisive%20victory%20sends%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20allies%20in%20the%20NDA%3A%20there%20can%20be%20no%20rearrangement%20of%20the%20pecking%20order.%20Although%20the%20two%20crucial%20supporting%20parties%20in%20the%20coalition-the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)-have%20been%20less%20vocal%20with%20their%20demands%2C%20Maharashtra's%20result%20will%20likely%20sober%20the%20party%20leadership%20and%20curb%20any%20Oliver%20Twist%20hunger%20pangs%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanchi's%20result%20was%20a%20major%20spoiler%20for%20the%20BJP's%20celebration%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20people's%20verdict%20delivered%20another%20subtle%20message.%20The%20JMM-led%20government%20employed%20welfare-oriented%20measures%20similar%20to%20those%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20reap%20a%20political%20harvest%2C%20while%20stalling%20the%20BJP's%20narrative%20of%20an%20imminent%20threat%20from%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators.%20The%20tribal%20population%20rejected%20this%20argument%20and%20spoke%20with%20their%20votes%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20outcome%20may%20offer%20some%20comfort%20to%20the%20Opposition%20and%20act%20as%20a%20speed%20bump%2C%20preventing%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20from%20cruising%20along%20with%20its%20core%20agenda.%20The%20session%20offers%20BJP%20leadership%20an%20opportunity%20to%20reassert%20its%20pole%20position%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20especially%20since%20its%20principal%20challenger%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20is%20less%20than%20equipped%20to%20check%20its%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732525140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fh2dc58k_modi-shah_625x300_18_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-fresh-fro