y%20team%20started%20work%20yesterday%2C%20a%20large%20group%20gathered%20near%20the%20mosque%20and%20started%20raising%20slogans.%20The%20situation%20escalated%20into%20a%20full-blown%20clash%20between%20cops%20and%20the%20protesters.%20Police%20had%20to%20use%20force%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Magistrate%20Rajendra%20Pesia%20said%20some%20people%20threw%20stones%20at%20police%2C%20but%20the%20situation%20was%20now%20in%20control.%20A%20total%20of%20seven%20cases%20have%20been%20registered%20against%20400-odd%20people%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20violence.%20The%20main%20Opposition%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20survey%20team%20was%20deliberately%20sent%20in%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20chaos%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20other%20side%20was%20not%20even%20heard%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20intentionally%20done%20to%20provoke%20emotions%20and%20avoid%20discussions%20on%20election%20rigging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20a%20day%20after%20the%20NDA%20scored%20big%20in%20the%20nine%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20bypolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20expressed%20condolences%20with%20the%20family%20members%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20violence.%20%26quot%3BThe%20administration%20did%20not%20hear%20all%20sides%20and%20acted%20insensitively.%20This%20spoiled%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20led%20to%20deaths%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20responsible%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20alleged%20the%20BJP%20of%20creating%20a%20rift%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20and%20said%20this%20was%20not%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20state%20or%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BI%20urge%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20intervene%20in%20this%20matter%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20peace%20and%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20sister%20and%20ne