20billion%20in%20H1%20financial%20year%202025%20to%20USD%2060%20billion%2C%20while%20gross%20debt%20grew%20by%20only%20USD%202%20billion.%20Equity%20now%20accounts%20for%2063%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebt%20maturities%20until%20the%202034%20financial%20year%20are%20comfortably%20manageable%20with%20current%20levels%2C%20even%20assuming%20no%20growth.%20This%20stability%20aligns%20with%20the%20group's%20long-term%20plans%20to%20invest%20USD%20100%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group's%20core%20infrastructure%20businesses%2C%20which%20include%20energy%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20utilities%2C%20remain%20the%20bedrock%20of%20its%20performance%2C%20contributing%2086.8%20per%20cent%20of%20H1%20for%20financial%20year%202025%20EBITDA.%20Emerging%20businesses%20in%20green%20energy%2C%20airports%2C%20and%20roads%20saw%20EBITDA%20growth%20of%2070.1%20per%20cent%20year-over-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20businesses%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Enterprises%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Passenger%20volumes%20across%20airports%20rose%206%20per%20cent%20%C2%A0YoY%2C%20while%20solar%20module%20sales%20jumped%2091%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOperational%20capacity%20increased%20by%2034%20per%20cent%20YoY%2C%20with%20construction%20commencing%20on%20a%20500%20MW%20hydro%20pump%20storage%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Energy%20Solutions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Expanded%20its%20transmission%20network%20by%202%2C760%20ckm%20and%20secured%20three%20new%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Ports%20and%20SEZ%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cargo%20volumes%20grew%209%20per%20cent%20year-over-year%2C%20while%20acquisitions%20bolstered%20operational%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Cements%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAcquisitions%20raised%20the%20group's%20cement%20capacity%20to%2097.8%20million%20tonne