20During%20the%20post-day%20press%20conference%20on%20Sunday%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20exchange%20and%20had%20a%20simple%20reply%20to%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20it%20at%20that%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20BGT%20series%20is%20Jaiswal's%20maiden%20tour%20of%20Australia.%20After%20a%20disappointing%20start%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20where%20he%20registered%20an%20eight-ball%20duck%2C%20Jaiswal%20held%20his%20composure%20and%20bounced%20back%20with%20a%20near-flawed%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022-year-old%20became%20the%20third%20Indian%20cricketer%20to%20slam%20a%20century%20on%20his%20maiden%20tour%20to%20Australia.%20He%20also%20overtook%20India%20legend%20Vijay%20Hazare's%20(1%2C420%20runs)%20tally%20and%20brought%20up%20the%20most%20runs%20by%20an%20Indian%20after%20his%20first%2015%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20four%20centuries%20already%20to%20his%20name%2C%20Jaiswal%20was%20asked%20to%20pick%20his%20favourite.%20He%20gave%20a%20heartwarming%20reply%20and%20gave%20equal%20importance%20to%20all%20of%20them.%20However%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20the%20one%20in%20Perth%20would%20be%20special%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20for%20me%2C%20all%20the%20centuries%20are%20amazing.%20But%20this%20will%20be%20special%20because%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20it.%20I%20worked%20hard%20in%20the%20practice%20session.%20I%20wanted%20to%20score%20runs%20in%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2015%20Tests%2C%20Jaiswal%20has%20scored%201%2C568%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2058.07%2C%20with%20four%20centuries%20and%20eight%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20214*.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732516140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F4pfo1a58_dassad_625x300_24_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fyashasvi-jaiswal-breaks-silence-on-coming-too-slow-exchange-with-mitchell-starc-felt-it-7095753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20dynamic%20opener%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20exchange%20with%20Australia's%20Mitchell%20Starc%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fyashasvi-jaiswal-breaks-silence-on-coming-too-slow-exchange-with-mitchell-starc-felt-it-7095753%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Slaps%2C%20Punches%20And%20Torn%20Shirts%2C%20UP%20Shopkeepers%20Fight%20Is%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20violent%20clash%20broke%20out%20between%20traders%20in%20Auraiya%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20over%20the%20placement%20of%20goods%20outside%20a%20shop.%20The%20confrontation%2C%20near%20Bhole%20Mandir%20in%20the%20Auraiya%20Sadar%20Kotwali%20area%2C%20escalated%20with%20the%20shopkeepers%20even%20picking%20sticks%20to%20beat%20each%20other%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road.%20The%20incident%20was%20captured%20on%20video%2C%20which%20soon%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20police%20have%20launched%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20obtained%20by%20NDTV%2C%20shows%20a%20chaotic%20scene%20as%20two%20men%20roll%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20busy%20road%2C%20furiously%20beating%20each%20other%20while%20a%20dog%20barks%20wildly%20at%20them.%20Two%20other%20men%20join%20the%20mayhem%2C%20tearing%20each%20other's%20shirts.%20Despite%20bystanders'%20intervention%2C%20the%20men%20continued%20to%20land%20slaps%C2%A0at%20each%20other%2C%20even%20as%20they%20were%20pulled%20apart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlok%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20the%20Additional%20Police%20Superintendent%20of%20Auraiya%2C%20explained%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20to%20NDTV.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20incident%20occurred%20when%20Anil%20Kumar%20and%20his%20neighbours%20%E2%80%93%20Pawan%20Kumar%2C%20Sunny%2C%20and%20Lucky%20%E2%80%93%20had%20an%20argument%20about%20placing%20goods%20outside%20a%20shop.%20This%20disagreement%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20violent%20physical%20fight%2C%20with%20both%20parties%20wielding%20sticks.%20The%20altercation%20spilt%20onto%20the%20road%2C%20where%20the%20traders%20were%20seen%20beating%20each%20other%20while%20lying%20on%20the%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Kumar%20filed%20a%20complaint.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20three%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20Pawan%20Kumar%2C%20Sunny%2C%20and%20Lucky%20%E2%80%93%20under%20section%20170%20of%20the%20BNS%20(Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha).%20As%20for%20Lucky%2C%20who%20is%20a%20minor%2C%20legal%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20per%20juvenile%20law%2C%20Mr%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20to%20mind%20a%20similar%20fight%20between%20UP%20shopkeepers%20back%20in%202021.%20Three%20years%20ago%2C%20an%20intense%20brawl%20broke%20out%20between%20chaat%20sellers%20in%20UP's%20Baghpat%2C%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20eight%20people.%20The%20fight%2C%20lasting%20nearly%2020%20minutes%2C%20erupted%20over%20a%20seemingly%20trivial%20matter%3A%20attracting%20customers%20to%20their%20stalls.%20The%20spectacle%20escalated%2C%20with%20two%20of%20the%20sellers%20exchanging%20blows%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20busy%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt's%20the%202nd%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20deadliest%20%E2%80%9CBattle%20of%20Papdi-Chaat%E2%80%9D%20fought%20at%20Baghpat%20that%20brought%20the%20world%20to%20its%20knees.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJSXvreC2n6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJSXvreC2n6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Yo%20Yo%20Funny%20Singh%20(%40moronhumor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmoronhumor%2Fstatus%2F1628386276402515969%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20standout%20moments%20of%20the%20fight%20was%20a%20chaat%20seller%2C%20who%20the%20internet%20later%20named%20%26quot%3BChaat%20Chacha.%26quot%3B%20Dressed%20in%20a%20kurta%20and%20with%20long%20mehendi-coloured%20hair%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20pinning%20down%20his%20rival%20during%20the%20tussle.%20After%20the%20fight%2C%20he%20became%20famous%20when%20his%20photo%20under%20detention%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20on%20this%20day%20in%202021%20AD%20that%20the%20battle%20of%20Baghpat%20was%20fought%20and%20won%20by%20Chaat%20Chaacha.%20All%20hail%20the%20supreme%20commander%2C%20the%20ruler%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Chaat%2C%20first%20of%20his%20name%2C%20last%20of%20his%20bravado...%20long%20live%20the%20devolution%20-%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBaghpat%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Baghpat%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2FcTu4kuth%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2FcTu4kuth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20noir%20(%40BanarasWallah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBanarasWallah%2Fstatus%2F1628348762144792576%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20image%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20be%20winking%2C%20but%20it%20was%20later%20speculated%20that%20his%20eye%20might%20have%20been%20swollen%20shut%20from%20the%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732515480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flo2kecc_up-shopkeepers-fight_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-slaps-punches-and-torn-shirts-up-shopkeepers-fight-is