0bill%20for%20that%20month%20was%20Rs%201%2C500%2C%20and%20they%20pay%20it%20through%20the%20SundayGrids%20platform%2C%20their%20energy%20credits%20are%20applied%2C%20reducing%20the%20bill%20to%20just%20Rs%2060.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-4-1732195942.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Community%20Solar%20saves%20electricity%20bills%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-4-1732195942.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-4-1732195942-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-4-1732195942-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-4-1732195942-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-4-1732195942-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381863%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Tarun%20goes%20on%20to%20claim%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20awesome%20benefit%20of%20the%20energy%20credits%20model%20is%20that%20since%20the%20sale%20of%20energy%20is%20tax-free%2C%20so%20is%20the%20solar%20savings%20on%20your%20electricity%20bills.%20At%2011.5%25%20XIRR%2C%20the%20savings%20yield%20from%20Digital%20Solar%20is%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20traditional%20rooftop%20solar%2C%20since%20instead%20of%20bespoke%205-10%20kW%20installations%2C%20most%20of%20our%20projects%20are%20100-200%20kW%20large%2C%20which%20gives%20us%20economies%20of%20scale%20and%20users%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20operational%20