3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20Odisha%20offered%20was%20the%20digitisation%20of%20NOCs%2C%20providing%20a%20solid%20database%20to%20identify%20violators%20regarding%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20a%20fire%20accident%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen%20here%2C%20which%20led%20them%20to%20be%20lethargic%20in%20applying%20for%20appropriate%20licences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%20that%20simple%20measures%20like%20planning%20the%20electrical%20load%20and%20investing%20in%20appropriate%20wiring%2C%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20switchboard%20placements%2C%20mapping%20the%20escape%20routes%2C%20placing%20a%20fire%20extinguisher%20in%20place%2C%20investing%20in%20a%20fire%20alarm%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20encouraging%20citizens%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%20before%20moving%20into%20a%20building%20can%20save%20lives%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264089%2Fdrdo-dare-to-dream-contest-winner-innovation-aircraft-accident-biodegradable%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20such%20disasters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20basics%20of%20fire%20safety%2C%20Venkitachalam%20discusses%20two%20primary%20criteria%3A%20the%20first%20is%20guidelines%20to%20be%20implemented%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20buildings%2C%20and%20the%20second%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20necessary%20measures%20are%20put%20in%20place%20by%20citizens%20to%20combat%20a%20fire%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20awareness%20programmes%20conducted%20in%20apartments%2C%20we%20try%20to%20educate%20people%20on%20their%20rights%20and%20duties%20when%20preventing%20an%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lifeline%20for%20burn%20victims%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID-19%2C%20India%20lost%20several%20lives%20to%20fires%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20hospitals%2C%20exposing%20critical%20gaps%20in%20fire%20safety%20and%20emergency%20preparedness.%20Recognising%20the%20urgency%20of%20addressing%20this%20issue%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20actively%20worked%20to%20improve%20care%20for%20burn%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20TD%20System%E2%80%99s%20CSR%20activity%2C%20the%20organisation%20launched%20the%20%23FireWatch101%20Project%20in%202023%2C%20focusing%20on%20equipping%20hospitals%20with%20essential%20facilities%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266757%2Fneehaari-mandali-burn-survivor-mission-saviour-trust-kerala-ngo-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etreat%20burn%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20effectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prognosis%20required%20for%20a%20burn%20injury%20to%20heal%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20requires%20daily%20dressing%20changes.%20This%20process%20is%20excruciating%20for%20patients%2C%20especially%20children%3B%20but%2C%20the%20number%20of%20government%20hospitals%20equipped%20with%20separate%20burn%20wards%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20scarce.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20to%20equip%20all%20government%20hospitals%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20ward%20dedicated%20to%20people%20affected%20due%20to%20a%20fire%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20points%20out%20that%20people%20often%20visit%20hospitals%20with%20kitchen%20accidents%2C%20electric%20burns%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20terms%20of%20prevention%20and%20cure%20is%20high%20as%20fire%20is%20never%20taken%20seriously%20unless%20something%20massive%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20Beyond%20Carlton%20team%20has%20successfully%20created%20awareness%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262996%2Fiit-in